{"tid":1441797,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[法律Mythbuster]警察係有權入屋苑拉人!私家地唔係結界!","createTime":"2019-08-10T17:56:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T19:06:27.000Z","uid":66994,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"284641b424a2031f9cb5d43457e3e5545ab8ff31","tid":1441797,"uid":66994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:56:49.000Z","msg":"剛才live見到將軍澳警察入村捉人, 令到我想check check一下一個流言:<br />\n究竟屋苑門口係咪結界, 警察冇warrant係咪唔入得?<br />\n<br />\n第232章 《警隊條例》 第50條 <br />\n(3)如任何警務人員<span style=\"color: green;\">有理由相信任何須予逮捕的人已進入或置身在某處</span>，則居住在該處或管理該處的人在該警務人員提出要求時，<span style=\"color: red;\">須容許該警務人員自由進入該處</span>，並給予一切合理的便利，以便他在內搜查。 <br />\n(4)如未能根據第(3)款獲准進入該處，則任何人在根據手令行事的情況下，<span style=\"color: red;\">及在本可發出手令但為免使須予逮捕的人有機會逃離警務人員而未取得該手令的情況下，該人進入該處及在內搜查，乃屬合法</span>；該人如在妥為宣告其所具權能、目的及內進的要求後，仍無其他方法獲准內進時，則他為得以進入該處而擊破任何地方的外部或內部的門或窗，均屬合法，不論該地方是屬於須予逮捕的人或其他人的。<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n如果本身係追捕過程個suspect跑左入屋苑, 執行上係依度要分2個情況:<br />\n(1) 屋苑私家地area, 但係唔駛保安開門<br />\n(2) 屋苑入左大閘/玻璃門area<br />\n係(1)情況之下警察係可以跑過私家地條界繼續追捕, 根據第(4)條入屋苑拉人/搜人<br />\n係(2)情況下警察係需要問保安先, 當然係同保安周旋時候個suspect唔知去左邊既可能性都係有既<br />\n所以suspect入左屋苑唔等於唔拉得個suspect, 特別係當追捕時個suspect入屋苑<br />\n警察係追捕疑犯<span style=\"color: red;\">唔需要</span>係屋苑門口拉break<br />\n反而疑犯入左屋苑就難追捕既原因係按照第(3)款提出要求既過程中不獲批準進入, 或者獲批準進入之後個疑犯唔知去左邊度<br />\n利申: 純條文分析, 不構成任何建議"},{"pid":"f83fb3932b7e226b86c277b647f70d32f70974fa","tid":1441797,"uid":66994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:58:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b14d9452d8375327158c48617674a8fac51f0ee2","tid":1441797,"uid":66994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"177583bc6bd48c8508411070cbea0f18afeedb2d","tid":1441797,"uid":66994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:02:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d029f1af7f53dae63fcbff021206b9fcf19834e6","tid":1441797,"uid":144084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:02:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"029d114e39f5a00eaea1e5826608df9d28a7df42","tid":1441797,"uid":103794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:03:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><a href=\"https://t.me/hkpestcontrolspray\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkpestcontrolspray&d=y7g0wjbeyFmnVC7InFCgMuzsNYmc6RwURZU94nRINXI%3D&h=4f47078b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkpestcontrolspray</a><br />\n一齊report group<br />\n呢個group 好多大頭相😱</span></span>"},{"pid":"e6b2c1338c7daea048a4ea6b758cd42e87b6e796","tid":1441797,"uid":66994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:04:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"865712e6acdc6e4cd922374255ff4650d72608cb","tid":1441797,"uid":66994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:06:12.000Z","msg":"我知依個好掃興, 但係一定一定要spread出去<br />\n如果唔係好多人會無辜落單"},{"pid":"732bca06b9a321814f07964acfd7e2b19a931433","tid":1441797,"uid":147434,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:06:29.000Z","msg":"你唔識就唔好再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n狗要無搜查令入私人地方拉人一定要好明確指出拉邊個同佢犯左咩罪行<br />\n如果UP唔出就可以唔俾入"},{"pid":"61e3799cc49aabc1194f1e1af58a3439da3057ce","tid":1441797,"uid":66994,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"732bca06b9a321814f07964acfd7e2b19a931433","tid":1441797,"uid":147434,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:06:29.000Z","msg":"你唔識就唔好再推<img sr